{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"NIUKASIER2","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["A Paean for Peace\n\n<size=45>Perfection and Peace<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"story-1","say":"*knock* *knock*","dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"While working with Newcastle in the office, I heard a knock at the door.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Master, sincerest apologies for interrupting your work.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202080},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Newcastle, there's something I would like your help with...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202080},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"say":"Is it about that warehouse?","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":1},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","actor":202190},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Indeed.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202080},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It should be fine as long you clean it up afterwards. You should take care of the rest as you see fit.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202190},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Understood. Thank you.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202080},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"After exchanging a few pleasantries, Sheffield bowed politely and left the office.","dir":1,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"What was that just now...?"}]},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"There's a slight issue with one of the old warehouses.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202190},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Nobody had time to clean it, so Sheffield and I suggested to Belfast that we might take care of it.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202190},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"As for Belfast... Well, if the Head Maid was to handle it, nobody would be leaving until every single item in the warehouse were inventoried and listed.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202190},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Even if all the Royal Maids were to help out, we'd struggle to complete a project of that scope.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202190},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But with just Sheffield and me, the two of us would be enough to get things to a satisfactory state.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202190},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"That Belfast will settle for nothing less than perfection, anything else be damned.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"However, there are situations in which the pursuit of perfection is not the best way to get things done.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Oh, pardon me. I apologize for boring you with my personal matters.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202190},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"blackBg":true,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"What I now pursue is not \"perfection,\" but rather \"peace.\"","actor":202190}]}